<title>USA: Lucent joins digital television effort.</title>
<headline>Lucent joins digital television effort.</headline>
<dateline>NEW YORK 1997-08-12</dateline>
<text>
<p>Lucent Technologies Inc. said on Tuesday that it will join with Compaq Computer Corp., Intel Corp. and Microsoft Corp. to speed the convergence of personal computers and television sets, using digital technology.</p>
<p>Lucent said in a news release that the four companies hope to develop affordably priced digital television products and services by the fall of 1998, allowing broadcasters to send video, audio and data transmissions to home televisions and personal computers.</p>
